@startmindmap
<style>
:depth(0) {
    BackgroundColor #FF5F46
    LineColor #FF5F46
    FontColor #ffffff
    LineThickness 3.0
}
:depth(1) {
    BackgroundColor #0078D4
    LineColor #0078D4
    LineThickness 3.0
    FontColor #FFFFFF
}
:depth(2) {
    BackgroundColor #ffb900
    LineColor #ffb900
    LineThickness 3.0
    FontColor #000000
}
boxless {
    FontColor #000000
}
</style>
* Notification\nEvents
** Start
***_ Job run begins
***_ Confirms scheduled job started
** Success
***_ Job completes successfully
***_ Trigger downstream processes
** Failure
***_ Job terminates with error
***_ Initiate incident response
** Duration Warning
***_ Run exceeds threshold
***_ Performance degradation alert
** Streaming Backlog
***_ Backlog exceeds threshold 10 min
***_ Streaming job health indicator
** Note
***_ "Succeeded with failures" = success
***_ Configure Success for partial failures
@endmindmap
